          <h1 id="Accessibility annotations for VA.gov applications">Accessibility annotations for VA.gov applications</h1>
          
          <div class="va-introtext" markdown="1">
            Accessibility annotations (called “annotations” in this document) are notes we add to our mockups to communicate meaning, behaviors, and interactions in the design or application.
          </div>
          
          
            
<nav aria-labelledby="on-this-page" class="site-on-this-page">
  <dl class="site-on-this-page__list">
    <dt id="on-this-page" role="heading" aria-level="2" class="site-on-this-page__title">
